<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-5922] CompileStatic: long loses type when bitwise OR applied to it</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-5922</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;@groovy.transform.CompileStatic
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;Test {
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt;[] data
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; topMask
    
  void doSomething() {
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt; mask = 0
    mask = mask | 0x1L
    data[ 0 ] = data[ 0 ] | mask
  }
}

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Test()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Gives the error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;[Static type checking] - Cannot assign value of type java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Number&lt;/span&gt; to variable of type &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A workaround is to add a cast:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    data[ 0 ] = data[ 0 ] | (&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt;)mask
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But I think that might cause &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-5921&quot; title=&quot;BUG! exception in phase &amp;#39;class generation&amp;#39; while poping argument from operand stack tracker&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;GROOVY-5921&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;GROOVY-5921&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to rear its head again...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Investigating&lt;/p&gt;</description>
