                            <comment id="14473957" author="andre.steingress" created="Mon, 21 Jan 2013 05:02:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;StaticTypeCheckingVisitor#getResultType(...) doesn&apos;t unwrap from java.lang.Long to long. Therefore, the inferred type of mask is java.lang.Long. (long | java.lang.Long) in the end leads to taking the return type from the DGM.or(Number, Number) method.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is a pull request: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/pull/122&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/groovy/groovy-core/pull/122&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
